        dd <ruby>𣍐<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㆤ˫/ㆠㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>堪<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㆰ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>得<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>考<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>驗<rt>&thinsp;ㆣ丨ㆰ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>考<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>驗<rt>&thinsp;ㆣ丨ㆰ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>食<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄚㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>力<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄚㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>擋<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㆲ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>𣍐<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㆤ˫/ㆠㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>住<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>柱<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>𣍐<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㆤ˫/ㆠㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>住<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)。
